metadata.name: The Storm Shall Pass
metadata.description:
We all have storms to navigate.  Threatening clouds will eventually give way to brighter days ahead.  Bring me that horizon.

This 1/1 image was taken at Gnarabup Beach on the Indian Ocean in Western Australia.  WA is one of the most beautiful places in the world.
